WEBVTT

00:00:35.900 --> 00:00:38.600
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.633 --> 00:00:41.333
=Episode 26=

00:00:51.700 --> 00:00:52.400
Young Master Chang.

00:00:52.933 --> 00:00:54.700
Your voice-changing pill really works.

00:00:56.433 --> 00:00:57.166
Young Duke.

00:00:58.266 --> 00:01:00.766
Why did you ask me to help
with this act?

00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:02.833
Because of Feng Fuliu,

00:01:03.733 --> 00:01:05.166
Bingfan has been trapped
in her own head lately.

00:01:05.766 --> 00:01:07.266
If she stays this reckless,

00:01:07.533 --> 00:01:08.566
she will never catch Leng Xin.

00:01:09.500 --> 00:01:10.833
I wanted her to snap out of

00:01:10.933 --> 00:01:11.866
this hatred quickly

00:01:12.266 --> 00:01:13.000
and calm down.

00:01:13.266 --> 00:01:14.033
That is why I asked for your help.

00:01:15.933 --> 00:01:16.800
I don't mind.

00:01:17.900 --> 00:01:19.933
I got to help my friend find peace.

00:01:22.100 --> 00:01:23.833
I will keep my promise to you.

00:01:24.666 --> 00:01:25.833
The case file you want to destroy,

00:01:26.600 --> 00:01:27.833
I will find a chance to destroy it
for you.

00:01:28.900 --> 00:01:29.800
Thank you, Young Duke.

00:01:30.933 --> 00:01:31.633
No need.

00:01:34.933 --> 00:01:36.433
Now that you have shed
that thief's skin,

00:01:38.866 --> 00:01:40.533
be Chief Squad Leader Hua properly.

00:01:57.033 --> 00:01:57.600
Eat up.

00:01:57.666 --> 00:01:59.266
We are on duty this afternoon.

00:01:59.533 --> 00:02:00.400
Have some more.

00:02:00.400 --> 00:02:01.133
Eat more of this.

00:02:01.166 --> 00:02:01.833
Pass me some too.

00:02:01.900 --> 00:02:02.633
(The Talismanist: Leng Xin's Device)
This is good for health.

00:02:02.666 --> 00:02:04.366
(The Talismanist: Leng Xin's Device)

00:02:04.400 --> 00:02:05.233
I'm exhausted.

00:02:05.233 --> 00:02:06.166
Exactly.

00:02:09.766 --> 00:02:10.666
What?

00:02:11.333 --> 00:02:14.366
The Talismanist: Leng Xin's Device.

00:02:31.500 --> 00:02:33.066
Strange. What's going on?

00:02:33.266 --> 00:02:34.433
What's wrong with her?

00:02:35.866 --> 00:02:37.200
Did she get lost in the book?

00:02:39.666 --> 00:02:40.866
She is completely possessed.

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:09.966
Leng Xin.

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:11.233
I will kill you!

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:12.833
I'm not Leng Xin!

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:15.166
Leng Xin!

00:03:16.366 --> 00:03:17.266
I will kill you!

00:03:17.266 --> 00:03:17.666
I'm not Leng Xin!

00:03:24.733 --> 00:03:26.166
Zhou, pull them apart!

00:03:26.700 --> 00:03:27.566
What are you waiting for?

00:03:28.900 --> 00:03:29.466
Pull them apart!

00:03:29.500 --> 00:03:30.666
Let go!

00:03:32.066 --> 00:03:32.933
Have you lost your mind?

00:03:33.366 --> 00:03:34.533
I was only sparring with you!

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:35.866
But you tried to kill me!

00:03:35.933 --> 00:03:37.100
Shen Bingfan, what are you doing?

00:03:37.366 --> 00:03:37.900
Unbelievable...

00:03:37.933 --> 00:03:39.000
Forget it, Bingfan.

00:03:39.033 --> 00:03:40.400
- She went too far.
- Yes.

00:03:40.400 --> 00:03:41.433
Come on. To the clinic.

00:03:42.166 --> 00:03:43.000
Are you all right?

00:03:43.266 --> 00:03:44.000
Go, go.

00:03:44.266 --> 00:03:45.100
Move along.

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:46.800
Let's be careful.

00:03:46.833 --> 00:03:47.733
Everyone, clear out.

00:03:50.700 --> 00:03:52.100
You are too tight.

00:03:54.166 --> 00:03:55.900
Leng Xin has killed in front
of me again and again.

00:03:56.700 --> 00:03:58.566
I just don't want another regret.

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:00.333
There is that stubborn temper again.

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:01.833
You are not

00:04:02.833 --> 00:04:05.166
a lone bounty hunter
in the martial world anymore.

00:04:05.666 --> 00:04:06.233
Who are you now?

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:08.333
You are a Jinyiwei Baihu.

00:04:09.066 --> 00:04:10.000
We have numbers,

00:04:10.200 --> 00:04:10.966
and we stand together.

00:04:11.600 --> 00:04:13.266
We can take Leng Xin down.

00:04:14.333 --> 00:04:16.233
You always find a way to comfort me.

00:04:17.100 --> 00:04:18.033
You need to relax.

00:04:18.533 --> 00:04:19.766
I will take you on an outing tomorrow.

00:04:21.266 --> 00:04:21.633
No.

00:04:22.533 --> 00:04:23.933
I need to train properly.

00:04:40.333 --> 00:04:41.200
Who is playing the flute?

00:04:43.666 --> 00:04:44.600
A beauty beneath the moon,

00:04:45.666 --> 00:04:46.833
dancing to the flute.

00:04:47.500 --> 00:04:48.566
That is quite a sight.

00:04:49.900 --> 00:04:50.500
It's you!

00:04:51.266 --> 00:04:52.300
You were training so hard,

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:53.766
so I used my flute

00:04:54.733 --> 00:04:55.666
to give you a little guidance.

00:04:56.700 --> 00:04:58.266
Leng Xin beat you too.

00:04:58.566 --> 00:04:59.500
What gives you the right to guide me?

00:05:00.400 --> 00:05:01.900
Victory and defeat are part of battle.

00:05:02.200 --> 00:05:03.966
Don't grow arrogant in victory
or despair in defeat.

00:05:04.400 --> 00:05:06.666
That is the secret
to mastering yourself and winning.

00:05:07.733 --> 00:05:09.133
You are restless,

00:05:09.900 --> 00:05:10.900
rushing for quick progress.

00:05:11.700 --> 00:05:12.600
You can't even beat me.

00:05:13.200 --> 00:05:14.266
How will you beat Leng Xin?

00:05:14.666 --> 00:05:15.833
I can't beat you?

00:05:16.766 --> 00:05:17.633
Want to try?

00:05:18.433 --> 00:05:19.600
Don't use footwork if you dare.

00:05:21.900 --> 00:05:22.800
Fine. I won't.

00:05:38.733 --> 00:05:39.666
How is this possible?

00:05:40.033 --> 00:05:42.066
You are impatient and desperate to win.

00:05:42.600 --> 00:05:43.700
Before you even strike,

00:05:44.233 --> 00:05:45.500
you are already full of openings.

00:05:49.533 --> 00:05:50.466
If you want to break through

00:05:51.200 --> 00:05:52.066
and defeat Leng Xin,

00:05:53.033 --> 00:05:54.466
meet me at Qizi Lake tomorrow night.

00:06:25.600 --> 00:06:26.166
You came.

00:06:27.100 --> 00:06:28.266
Why did you ask me here?

00:06:29.266 --> 00:06:31.433
To teach you how to break
Leng Xin's killing move.

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:33.700
You can break Leng Xin's swordplay?

00:06:36.833 --> 00:06:37.933
Your Water-Cutting Blade

00:06:38.200 --> 00:06:39.466
was made to counter

00:06:39.566 --> 00:06:41.233
Leng Xin's Thirteen Fatal Blades.

00:06:42.366 --> 00:06:43.800
Your school favors softness over force

00:06:44.233 --> 00:06:45.433
with only female disciples.

00:06:46.100 --> 00:06:48.100
But your blade work has become
too forceful,

00:06:48.933 --> 00:06:50.533
so you can't bring out its true power.

00:06:53.600 --> 00:06:54.600
I see.

00:06:58.533 --> 00:06:59.100
Attack me.

00:07:02.833 --> 00:07:04.066
That move is too hard.

00:07:06.666 --> 00:07:08.066
This one can soften the force.

00:07:11.733 --> 00:07:12.600
Remember.

00:07:13.033 --> 00:07:14.533
Sometimes, softness overcomes strength,

00:07:15.200 --> 00:07:16.533
and that can win the fight.

00:08:04.633 --> 00:08:06.066
(Northern Bureau)

00:08:06.066 --> 00:08:06.500
(Northern Bureau)
Bingfan.

00:08:06.866 --> 00:08:08.100
You are not coming back
to Chong'er Pavilion for dinner again?

00:08:08.866 --> 00:08:09.766
Don't wait for me.

00:08:10.333 --> 00:08:11.333
What have you been doing lately?

00:08:11.333 --> 00:08:12.666
You go out every night.

00:08:12.900 --> 00:08:14.333
Don't ask. I have work to do.

00:08:16.200 --> 00:08:16.533
But...

00:08:24.500 --> 00:08:25.900
He never misses an appointment.

00:08:26.766 --> 00:08:27.966
Did something happen?

00:08:30.266 --> 00:08:30.800
Feng Fuliu!

00:08:57.900 --> 00:08:58.633
You ambushed me!

00:08:59.500 --> 00:09:00.933
That is what Leng Xin does best.

00:09:01.366 --> 00:09:03.266
Your martial skills
have improved greatly,

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:04.533
and your mind is much steadier.

00:09:05.233 --> 00:09:06.133
If you face Leng Xin again,

00:09:06.700 --> 00:09:07.400
you can fight him.

00:09:09.533 --> 00:09:10.300
But

00:09:11.233 --> 00:09:12.500
I'm afraid I still can't beat him.

00:09:12.933 --> 00:09:14.033
You have your people.

00:09:14.366 --> 00:09:15.266
Besides,

00:09:15.833 --> 00:09:16.766
I will help you too.

00:09:21.766 --> 00:09:23.166
Why are you so good to me?

00:09:26.433 --> 00:09:27.866
I like the way you look when you smile.

00:09:41.100 --> 00:09:42.466
Now, that is a beauty's smile.

00:10:01.700 --> 00:10:02.866
Thank you for always helping me.

00:10:10.866 --> 00:10:11.700
I knew it!

00:10:13.166 --> 00:10:13.900
You liar!

00:10:16.733 --> 00:10:17.466
Let me explain.

00:10:17.733 --> 00:10:18.500
What is there to explain?

00:10:19.533 --> 00:10:20.266
Give me a chance.

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:21.500
I will explain everything.

00:10:22.233 --> 00:10:22.466
Fine.

00:10:23.200 --> 00:10:24.233
Then explain this.

00:10:24.366 --> 00:10:25.933
Why would a Young Duke become a thief?

00:10:26.233 --> 00:10:26.933
I didn't.

00:10:27.166 --> 00:10:29.400
I only pretended to be Feng Fuliu
to help you get unstuck.

00:10:30.266 --> 00:10:31.200
Pretended to be Feng Fuliu?

00:10:31.700 --> 00:10:32.300
You still will not admit it.

00:10:32.333 --> 00:10:33.100
You are Feng Fuliu.

00:10:33.100 --> 00:10:33.866
I'm not.

00:10:36.166 --> 00:10:37.033
I will tell you the truth.

00:10:37.500 --> 00:10:38.200
Lately,

00:10:38.366 --> 00:10:40.100
you were trapped in your own head
and wouldn't listen to anyone.

00:10:40.500 --> 00:10:41.933
I was afraid you would train yourself
into madness.

00:10:42.333 --> 00:10:43.533
So I pretended to be Feng Fuliu

00:10:43.666 --> 00:10:44.700
to help you untie that knot.

00:10:45.333 --> 00:10:46.433
Do I look like a child to you?

00:10:46.766 --> 00:10:48.266
Your fighting styles are exactly
the same.

00:10:53.166 --> 00:10:54.600
That is because I learn
from every school.

00:10:54.833 --> 00:10:56.333
I have studied countless martial arts
since childhood.

00:10:56.733 --> 00:10:58.333
Of course I know the styles
of the world.

00:10:58.666 --> 00:10:59.733
Feng Fuliu's style

00:10:59.900 --> 00:11:00.633
is no exception.

00:11:02.033 --> 00:11:02.466
I don't believe you.

00:11:05.666 --> 00:11:06.366
If you don't believe me,

00:11:07.400 --> 00:11:08.266
then arrest me.

00:11:10.100 --> 00:11:10.833
You think I won't?

00:11:28.100 --> 00:11:29.166
I just want the truth.

00:11:30.233 --> 00:11:31.333
Are you Feng Fuliu or not?

00:11:38.600 --> 00:11:39.300
I'm not.

00:11:52.566 --> 00:11:53.133
Bingfan.

00:11:54.266 --> 00:11:55.200
Sometimes,

00:11:56.100 --> 00:11:57.000
people have no choice.

00:11:58.600 --> 00:12:01.033
Even when you are born
into power and rank,

00:12:03.600 --> 00:12:04.766
before fate,

00:12:05.666 --> 00:12:06.500
all you are left with

00:12:07.100 --> 00:12:08.033
is helplessness.

00:12:10.066 --> 00:12:11.166
So pretending to be Feng Fuliu

00:12:11.933 --> 00:12:13.000
was also because you had no choice?

00:12:14.700 --> 00:12:15.700
I only wanted to help you.

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:17.933
You have to believe me.

00:12:28.266 --> 00:12:28.633
Fine.

00:12:31.366 --> 00:12:32.900
If this is a beautiful lie,

00:12:37.700 --> 00:12:38.366
then I believe you.

00:12:50.766 --> 00:12:52.100
When this is over,

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:55.900
I will tell you the whole truth.

00:12:57.733 --> 00:12:58.333
After that,

00:13:00.200 --> 00:13:00.733
no more secrets.

00:13:01.733 --> 00:13:02.433
Only the truth of my heart.

00:13:03.166 --> 00:13:04.266
After we catch Leng Xin?

00:13:13.833 --> 00:13:14.266
Snake!

00:13:38.466 --> 00:13:45.266
♪Yet in the crowd, we brush past♪

00:13:45.833 --> 00:13:48.866
♪Only then did I understand fate♪

00:13:48.866 --> 00:13:52.400
♪Was hidden in the day we met♪

00:13:53.500 --> 00:13:55.566
♪A fate that cannot be severed♪

00:13:55.766 --> 00:13:56.100
Search!

00:13:56.100 --> 00:13:56.366
Yes.

00:14:01.533 --> 00:14:02.066
Guan.

00:14:04.733 --> 00:14:05.500
Guan, look.

00:14:08.533 --> 00:14:09.066
This is the place.

00:14:10.400 --> 00:14:10.833
What?

00:14:11.433 --> 00:14:13.366
You found Leng Xin's hideout?

00:14:14.533 --> 00:14:14.900
Yes.

00:14:15.566 --> 00:14:17.066
Thanks to Constable Guan's
day-and-night search,

00:14:17.433 --> 00:14:18.966
we found where Leng Xin is hiding.

00:14:19.200 --> 00:14:19.466
Good!

00:14:20.033 --> 00:14:20.466
Good!

00:14:21.033 --> 00:14:21.533
Zuo Da! Jiang Biao!

00:14:21.900 --> 00:14:22.300
Yes!

00:14:22.833 --> 00:14:23.700
Gather the Jinyiwei at once!

00:14:24.166 --> 00:14:24.866
Have them assemble immediately!

00:14:25.366 --> 00:14:25.733
Yes!

00:14:26.866 --> 00:14:27.566
Jinyiwei,

00:14:27.700 --> 00:14:28.600
surround this place.

00:14:34.566 --> 00:14:35.000
My lord.

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:36.700
This is definitely it.

00:14:37.333 --> 00:14:37.833
Strange.

00:14:38.033 --> 00:14:39.700
Why is there no plaque on this manor?

00:14:41.900 --> 00:14:43.133
They must have something to hide.

00:14:44.033 --> 00:14:44.433
Jiang Biao.

00:14:44.666 --> 00:14:45.066
Yes.

00:14:45.100 --> 00:14:45.600
Break down the door.

00:14:47.900 --> 00:14:48.233
Wait.

00:14:49.733 --> 00:14:50.000
My lord.

00:14:50.366 --> 00:14:50.600
My lord.

00:14:51.100 --> 00:14:51.500
Look.

00:14:51.866 --> 00:14:53.866
(Meizhen House)

00:14:56.600 --> 00:14:57.000
Mei...

00:14:57.266 --> 00:14:58.100
Withdraw. Now!

00:14:58.433 --> 00:14:58.833
My lord.

00:14:59.400 --> 00:15:00.800
Leng Xin, that murderer,
is right inside.

00:15:00.833 --> 00:15:01.433
Why withdraw?

00:15:02.866 --> 00:15:03.800
One day, you people

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:04.866
will get me killed.

00:15:05.500 --> 00:15:06.000
Leave!

00:15:06.000 --> 00:15:06.500
Go!

00:15:15.900 --> 00:15:16.300
Guokai.

00:15:16.933 --> 00:15:19.500
Didn't you take a large force
to arrest Leng Xin?

00:15:22.066 --> 00:15:22.433
My lord.

00:15:23.066 --> 00:15:24.133
This matter would be difficult

00:15:24.666 --> 00:15:27.233
even for you.

00:15:29.200 --> 00:15:32.366
What could possibly be beyond me?

00:15:34.366 --> 00:15:35.100
Meizhen House.

00:15:38.833 --> 00:15:41.100
What exactly is this Meizhen House?

00:15:42.233 --> 00:15:44.233
It makes the entire Northern Bureau

00:15:44.233 --> 00:15:45.333
too afraid to speak

00:15:45.733 --> 00:15:46.600
and jump at shadows.

00:15:47.200 --> 00:15:48.533
Exactly.

00:15:49.200 --> 00:15:52.133
Even the mighty Northern Bureau

00:15:53.233 --> 00:15:54.766
is scared out of its wits.

00:15:55.266 --> 00:15:57.033
The whole Northern Bureau is on edge,

00:15:57.500 --> 00:15:58.366
terrified at the mention of it.

00:15:58.833 --> 00:16:01.166
No one dares talk
about arresting Leng Xin anymore.

00:16:01.766 --> 00:16:02.433
It seems

00:16:03.033 --> 00:16:04.133
Meizhen House's backing

00:16:04.400 --> 00:16:05.466
runs very deep.

00:16:05.600 --> 00:16:07.300
You have been in the capital for years,

00:16:07.366 --> 00:16:08.800
and you have never heard of it?

00:16:09.100 --> 00:16:09.933
No.

00:16:11.200 --> 00:16:13.700
With such powerful backing,

00:16:14.700 --> 00:16:15.933
Meizhen House must be tied to the court.

00:16:17.166 --> 00:16:18.033
I will ask Chang Beiming.

00:16:18.166 --> 00:16:19.700
That Young Duke

00:16:20.033 --> 00:16:21.966
is too sharp for that. Ask him?

00:16:23.000 --> 00:16:23.666
Then what do we do?

00:16:24.166 --> 00:16:27.600
If this has to do
with powerful court nobles,

00:16:28.533 --> 00:16:29.766
maybe those three men

00:16:30.066 --> 00:16:30.766
know something.

00:16:31.733 --> 00:16:32.733
Meizhen House

00:16:33.233 --> 00:16:35.233
is the most mysterious pleasure house
in the capital.

00:16:36.333 --> 00:16:37.100
A pleasure house?

00:16:37.600 --> 00:16:38.800
More powerful than Chong'er Pavilion?

00:16:38.833 --> 00:16:40.366
Compared with Meizhen House,

00:16:40.866 --> 00:16:42.100
Chong'er Pavilion is nothing.

00:16:42.600 --> 00:16:43.100
And

00:16:43.666 --> 00:16:44.600
they say

00:16:44.866 --> 00:16:46.933
only high officials and nobles

00:16:47.533 --> 00:16:49.566
can freely enter
and enjoy themselves there.

00:16:50.566 --> 00:16:51.966
Everyone who goes in and out

00:16:52.933 --> 00:16:54.000
is rich or powerful,

00:16:54.566 --> 00:16:55.933
with a distinguished background.

00:16:56.266 --> 00:16:58.666
Lu Guokai is only a fourth-rank
Commissioner.

00:16:59.266 --> 00:17:00.600
How would he dare offend Meizhen House?

00:17:02.366 --> 00:17:03.600
Rumor has it

00:17:04.100 --> 00:17:06.600
that one of the owners
behind Meizhen House

00:17:06.866 --> 00:17:09.600
is none other than Prince Fu himself.

00:17:17.266 --> 00:17:17.833
Baihu Shen.

00:17:18.066 --> 00:17:19.433
You can't go in.

00:17:23.166 --> 00:17:23.600
My lord.

00:17:24.100 --> 00:17:26.266
I really couldn't stop Baihu Shen.

00:17:28.200 --> 00:17:28.566
Yes.

00:17:35.233 --> 00:17:36.566
I'm ill.

00:17:37.100 --> 00:17:38.433
I'm sick.

00:17:38.833 --> 00:17:41.733
Can't you show a sick man some mercy?

00:17:41.866 --> 00:17:42.633
My lord, this illness...

00:17:43.400 --> 00:17:44.833
Was it caused by Meizhen House?

00:17:54.333 --> 00:17:55.266
What do you know?

00:17:57.266 --> 00:17:59.766
A pleasure house for powerful men
to indulge themselves

00:18:00.233 --> 00:18:01.766
makes a man as powerful
as the Left Commander

00:18:02.100 --> 00:18:03.300
and head of the Northern Bureau

00:18:03.566 --> 00:18:04.900
hide in his room.

00:18:05.233 --> 00:18:06.466
What do you know now?

00:18:06.900 --> 00:18:08.400
It is one pleasure house,

00:18:09.000 --> 00:18:10.700
but its power reaches the heavens.

00:18:11.366 --> 00:18:12.933
That just means a prince is involved.

00:18:13.033 --> 00:18:15.133
A prince is involved.
You think that's nothing?

00:18:15.933 --> 00:18:18.800
"When a prince breaks the law,
he is punished like a commoner."

00:18:18.833 --> 00:18:20.366
That is a lie told to children.

00:18:20.733 --> 00:18:21.966
Then, are Ming laws

00:18:22.100 --> 00:18:23.100
only made for commoners?

00:18:23.366 --> 00:18:25.033
Ming laws are made by imperial power.

00:18:25.333 --> 00:18:28.033
And you are trying to investigate
the very people who make them.

00:18:28.666 --> 00:18:29.900
Then, before imperial power,

00:18:30.066 --> 00:18:31.266
does justice mean nothing?

00:18:47.833 --> 00:18:51.000
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:51.366 --> 00:18:54.733
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:55.000 --> 00:18:58.000
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:58.000 --> 00:19:01.400
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:19:02.500 --> 00:19:05.700
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:19:06.133 --> 00:19:09.466
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:19:10.033 --> 00:19:12.233
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:12.266 --> 00:19:16.300
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:16.300 --> 00:19:20.166
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:20.166 --> 00:19:23.900
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:24.200 --> 00:19:26.100
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:26.133 --> 00:19:30.666
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:30.966 --> 00:19:32.466
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:32.466 --> 00:19:34.833
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:34.833 --> 00:19:38.700
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:38.700 --> 00:19:41.000
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:41.033 --> 00:19:46.033
♪And run toward this vast life♪